OL,3,CThe two men now expected to lead
OL,4,CLabour both ends of the M4
OL,6,FKen Skates MS and Andy Burnham MP
OL,7,Fcould be a likely partnership as
OL,8,Fnominations for the Welsh and UK
OL,9,FLabour party leadership get underway.
OL,11,FBut why are there two party leadership
OL,12,Felections on-going at the same time?
OL,14,FFormer First Minister, Eluned Morgan,
OL,15,Flost her seat in the Senedd election
OL,16,Fearlier this year, after which Ken
OL,17,FSkates was appointed as the interim
OL,18,FLabour leader.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
