OL,3,CThe two men now expected to lead
OL,4,CLabour both ends of the M4
OL,6,FAlso, in June Sir Kier Starmer
OL,7,Fannounced his resignation following
OL,8,Fconcerns raised by his party regarding
OL,9,Fhis ability to lead triggering a
OL,10,Fleadership contest.
OL,12,FThe Welsh Labour party has now pulled
OL,13,Fforward their election to match up
OL,14,Fwith the UK party's timetable.
OL,16,FNominations open Thursday 9 July
OL,17,Fmeaning the role of Prime Minister and
OL,18,FWelsh Labour leader will be up for
OL,19,Fgrabs.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
