OL,3,CThe two men now expected to lead
OL,4,CLabour both ends of the M4
OL,6,FAs it stands there is currently only
OL,7,Fone candidate up for each job - Skates
OL,8,Fand Burnham.
OL,10,FBoth contests will close nominations
OL,11,Fon July 16. Welsh Labour are yet to
OL,12,Fconfirm the timetable following
OL,13,Fclosure,
OL,15,FIt's anticipated if Andy Burnham wins
OL,16,Fthe contest he would be confirmed as
OL,17,FPrime Minister on July 20.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
