OL,3,CThe two men now expected to lead
OL,4,CLabour both ends of the M4
OL,6,FKen Skates, the current interim leader
OL,7,Ffor Welsh Labour is currently
OL,8,Funopposed and it seems unlikely that
OL,9,Fhe will face a challenger in this one
OL,10,Fman competition.
OL,12,FITV Cymru questioned Skates on his
OL,13,Frelationship with Burnham, he
OL,14,Fresponded: "I've known Andy for quite
OL,15,Fsome time now, we come from a similar
OL,16,Fbackground, I know what his passions
OL,17,Fare, I know what drives him".
OL,19,FHe continues: "I am confident that he
OL,20,Fwill be able to improve the lives of
OL,21,Fpeople across Wales".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
