PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1783673386
OL,3,CThe two men now expected to lead
OL,4,CLabour both ends of the M4
OL,6,FAt a recent session of First Minister
OL,7,FQuestions (FMQ's), leader of Reform UK
OL,8,FWales, Dan Thomas questioned Rhun ap
OL,9,FIorwerth on his abilities to build a
OL,10,Fstrong correspondence with Andy
OL,11,FBurnham and accused him of "not
OL,12,Fcommanding the respect Wales needs in
OL,13,Fthe First Minister".
OL,15,FA change in Welsh politics in imminent
OL,16,Fwith a new Prime Minister and new
OL,17,FWelsh Labour leader, which following
OL,18,Fthe turbulent elections in May, could
OL,19,Fcause another big shakeup.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/6
